    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Hexblade lets you choose from an expanded list of spells when you learn a warlock spell. The following spells are added to the warlock spell list for you.</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td>Spell Level</td>\n<td>Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.gFW5CNtbklkcYxen]{Shield}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.QjwVm4yS6NPrNfDq]{Wrathful Smite}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.UpVYFKrZYbb8KCYt]{Blur}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.SmHcPczugxpy3UXN]{Branding Smite}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.9B0luNcaaHSDAQps]{Blink}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.fEjWft78oYHZIlqe]{Elemental Weapon}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.Bj0TlGKPBuXI2OZW]{Phantasmal Killer}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.dQx9nQMpfb3fG9zM]{Staggering Smite}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.E8hBZqwiPTr7gtzw]{Banishing Smite}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.vUFQvX3V7qTqgqFE]{Cone of Cold}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
